data.description: Prime Location!  Close to schools, hospitals, shops, restaurants and more.  Come take a look at this multi-level home that includes 4 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms and  1 half bathroom.  Need more space?  This home has 2 additional spaces in the lower level for your home office/den/gym. With 3 living spaces,  this house has a spot for everyone!  Come relax on the beautiful large deck out back. New furnace and new AC in 2022! This home checks all the boxes plus seller is offering $3,000 flooring credit.  Make an appointment today.
